articles.author: Kathleen Magramo
articles.title: Singapore defends Taylor Swift’s exclusive Southeast Asia stop after neighbors cry foul - CNN
articles.description: Singapore is drawing fans from all over Southeast Asia and beyond to Taylor Swift’s Eras Tour, much to the annoyance of the city-state’s regional neighbors.
